high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the coffee table.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk over to the chair.
Put the blue credit card on the middle of the front edge of the seat of the chair.
Turn left and walk over to the small wooden table to the left of the couch.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the small wooden table.
Turn right and walk over to the chair with the credit card on its seat.
Put the credit card on the seat of the chair to the left of the card that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn to face your left
Pick up a credit card off of the table
Turn right, left and then turn to the right again to face the chair
Set the credit card down on the chair cushion
Turn to your left twice and then turn to your right to face a table
Pick up another credit card from this table
Return to where you were standing in front of the chair
Set the second credit card down next to the first
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards on a chair

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the coffee table, the side closest to the couch.
Pick up the credit card.
Turn right and walk to the chair.
Place the credit card on the chair, near the front and center of the cushion.
Turn around and veer right to the table in the right corner of the room.
Pick up the credit card on the table.
Turn around and walk back to the chair.
Place the credit card on the chair to the left of the other credit card.
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards on a chair.
